(285, 1, 23, 5, 'insert', '2014 Mercer TRS and Benefits Survey', '{&quot;category_id&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;mTeKuKAqH8f&quot;,&quot;is_home&quot;:false,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;2014 Mercer TRS and Benefits Survey&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;2014-mercer-trs-and-benefits-survey-mTeKuKAqH8f&quot;,&quot;description_vi&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;content_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;HAVE YOU EVER HAD CONCERNS ABOUT\\u2026&lt;\\/b&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ul type=\\&quot;disc\\&quot;&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 2.25pt;\\&quot;&gt;How competitive are our salary, allowances, bonuses, sales incentives versus market?&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 2.25pt;\\&quot;&gt;How competitive is our benefits package versus market?&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 2.25pt;\\&quot;&gt;How does our company remain competitive in pay and benefits offerings and yet operate within budget constraints?&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 2.25pt;\\&quot;&gt;How do other leading well-established companies maximize the use of their salary and benefits budget?&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\n\\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;MERCER \\u2013 TALENTNET\\u2019S TOTAL REMUNERATION SURVEY (TRS) &amp;amp; BENEFITS SURVEY REPORTS HAVE ALL THE SOLUTIONS FOR YOU.&lt;\\/b&gt;&lt;br \\/&gt;\\nMercer \\u2013 Talentnet\\u2019s TRS is known as the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;most comprehensive&lt;\\/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;reliable &lt;\\/b&gt;remuneration database in Vietnam market with 418 organizations across 13 industries participating in 2013, contributing compensation data of more than 142,000 employees.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br \\/&gt;\\nBesides TRS, Mercer \\u2013 Talentnet\\u2019s Benefits survey, with 278 participants across 9 industries, provides the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;most current&lt;\\/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;robust&lt;\\/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;benefits information on key supplementary benefits and HR practices.&l