(326, 1, 345, 5, 'edit', 'Dịch vụ giải pháp nhân sự: Dành cho nguời sử dụng lao động', '{&quot;category_id&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;AfBX2QxXm6&quot;,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;D\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p nh\\u00e2n s\\u1ef1: D\\u00e0nh cho ngu\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng lao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;dich-vu-giai-phap-nhan-su-danh-cho-nguoi-su-dung-lao-dong-AfBX2QxXm6&quot;,&quot;content_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;To allow you to focus on your core business activities, we can provide a complete staffing solutions package. This covers finding and recruiting employees for you, managing all labor\\u2013related issues during their employment, including labor management, insurance registration, personal income tax returns and year-end finalizations. We will also provide HR support and guidance to employees from the time they join until the time they leave, which will help maximize their effectiveness in their role.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Services Offered&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Search and selection of candidates based on companies\\u2019 requirements.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Provision of contractors to companies.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;On going HR Administration and Support&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Staff management&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Payroll - Insurance \\u2013 Taxation processing.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Additions and Deductions&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Maternity\\/Sick leave claims&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Termination payments&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Pay-slip summaries&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Provision of a replacement in the event of an employee resigning&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;name_en&quot;:&quot;Staffing Solution Service: For employers&quot;,&quot;slug_en&quot;:&quot;staffing-solution-service-for-employers--AfBX2QxXm6&quot;,&quot;content_en&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;To allow you to focus on your core business a