(327, 1, 345, 7, 'insert', 'Total Remuneration Survey (TRS)', '{&quot;category_id&quot;:&quot;3&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;5SS4xdrztKx&quot;,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;Total Remuneration Survey (TRS)&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;total-remuneration-survey-trs-5SS4xdrztKx&quot;,&quot;content_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Today''s Human Resource professionals are seeking solutions to build a consistent pay strategy. There is a need to maintain external competitiveness while maintaining internal equity. Mercer''s Total Remuneration Survey (TRS) collects compensation and typical benefits information to help you to:&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Gain understanding of key remuneration issues in your country&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Evaluate the competitive position of your company&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Access reliable, accurate and high quality market data anytime and anywhere through the web&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Obtain customized statistics that meet your needs using a robust pay database&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Make your pay packages more attractive by establishing competitive and cost effective compensation and benefits adjustments&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Identify areas for improvement in your attraction and retention process&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Plan compensation adjustments based on meaningful comparisons of remuneration practices&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;name_en&quot;:&quot;Total Remuneration Survey (TRS)&quot;,&quot;slug_en&quot;:&quot;total-remuneration-survey-trs--5SS4xdrztKx&quot;,&quot;content_en&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Today''s Human Resource professionals are seeking solutions to build a consistent pay strategy. There is a need to maintain external competitiveness while maintaining internal equity. Mercer''s Total Remuneration Survey (TRS) collects compensation and typical benefits information to help you to:&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Gain understanding of key remuneration issues in your