(373, 1, 361, 11, 'edit', 'v1234', '{&quot;function_id&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;industry_id&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;location_id&quot;:&quot;67&quot;,&quot;level_id&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;kt2INMjkUN&quot;,&quot;code&quot;:&quot;v1234&quot;,&quot;tags&quot;:1,&quot;hot&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;Tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng Ph\\u00f2ng Kinh Doanh Qu\\u1ea3ng C\\u00e1o&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;truong-phong-kinh-doanh-quang-cao-kt2INMjkUN&quot;,&quot;em_description_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2006, our client is one of the leading asset management companies. Please submit CV to &lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:career.solution@talentnet.vn\\&quot;&gt;career.solution@talentnet.vn&lt;\\/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:huynh.t.bich.nguyen@talentnet.vn\\&quot;&gt;huynh.t.bich.nguyen@talentnet.vn&lt;\\/a&gt; or contact directly to Ms. Huynh Thi Bich Nguyen at 62914188, ext: 520.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;job_description_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;- Conduct secondary research on trading portfolio stocks&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management in the reparation of documentation for rebalancing, switching, transactions, as well the buying-and-selling of securities.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Develop investment structures, on the basis of inputs from lawyers and collaborate with the Analyst and Investment Deal teams, for the preparation and execution of investments.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management in monitoring and reporting on the financial performance of the investments to BOD and clients.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Implement and document all trading investment proposals, which are approved for investment.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management to monitor and report on risks and risk mitigation.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Perform other tasks, as required by other Directors of Company.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Ensure the strict observation of Company corporate policies, establish and maintain the highest possible standards of ethics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;job_requirement_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;- Bachelor''s degree with distinction; MBA is preferable&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- At least 2 year experience in securities trading or investment related fields.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Strong analytical skills&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Good communication skill &amp;amp; teamwork&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Fluent in both written and spoken English&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- MS Office&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;salary_min_vi&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;salary_max_vi&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;name_en&quot;:&quot;Trader&quot;,&quot;slug_en&quot;:&quot;trader--kt2INMjkUN&quot;,&quot;em_description_en&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2006, our client is one of the leading asset management companies. Please submit CV to &lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:career.solution@talentnet.vn\\&quot;&gt;career.solution@talentnet.vn&lt;\\/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:huynh.t.bich.nguyen@talentnet.vn\\&quot;&gt;huynh.t.bich.nguyen@talentnet.vn&lt;\\/a&gt; or contact directly to Ms. Huynh Thi Bich Nguyen at 62914188, ext: 520.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;job_requirement_en&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;- Conduct secondary research on trading portfolio stocks&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management in the reparation of documentation for rebalancing, switching, transactions, as well the buying-and-selling of securities.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Develop investment structures, on the basis of inputs from lawyers and collaborate with the Analyst and Investment Deal teams, for the preparation and execution of investments.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management in monitoring and reporting on the financial performance of the investments to BOD and clients.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Implement and document all trading investment proposals, which are approved for investment.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Assist the Director of Portfolio Management to monitor and report on risks and risk mitigation.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Perform other tasks, as required by other Directors of Company.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Ensure the strict observation of Company corporate policies, establish and maintain the highest possible standards of ethics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;job_description_en&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;- Bachelor''s degree with distinction; MBA is preferable&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- At least 2 year experience in securities trading or investment related fields.&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Strong analytical skills&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Good communication skill &amp;amp; teamwork&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- Fluent in both written and spoken English&lt;br \\/&gt;\\n- MS Office&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&quot;,&quot;salary_min_en&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;salary_max_en&quot;:&quot;&quot;}', 1, '2014-07-11 17:50:30', '2014-07-11 17:50:30');
