(374, 1, 364, 8, 'edit', 'For Starting a Business in Vietnam', '{&quot;category_id&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;Mnwfk1jW1d&quot;,&quot;tags&quot;:3,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;For Starting a Business in Vietnam&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;for-starting-a-business-in-vietnam-Mnwfk1jW1d&quot;,&quot;description_vi&quot;:&quot;For a newly set-up company, it is no doubt that management team play an important role in starting up businesses in the first phase, especially for those possessing strong experiences in setting up new offices. They will help businesses much in recruiting the right talents, understanding Vietnamese business culture to deal with other partners and government offices, driving the key success factors at the soonest for the company development.&quot;,&quot;content_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;What are the most concerns when you are to set up new company in other countries?&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;The different working and business culture?&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;The understanding the new business and labor law?&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;The administration workload?&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;The recruitment of right person with appropriate capabilities?&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\n\\n&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: small;\\&quot;&gt;For a newly set-up company,&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\