(433, 1, 345, 1, 'edit', 'Dành cho nhân viên', '{&quot;category_id&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;ids&quot;:&quot;zO3AX7rZjh&quot;,&quot;name_vi&quot;:&quot;D\\u00e0nh cho nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean&quot;,&quot;slug_vi&quot;:&quot;danh-cho-nhan-vien-zO3AX7rZjh&quot;,&quot;content_vi&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Talentnet Executive Search Services. With more than 10 years of HR experience in setting international standards in the Vietnamese labor market, Talentnet\\u2019s dedicated Executive Search team has an unparalleled reach into this market. We deliver results by equipping experienced and driven consultants with state of the art technology. Working together with both large multinationals and well-regarded local companies, we are a renowned HR brand for both employers and professional talent. We are passionate about helping you find the professionals you need to deliver your business strategy.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n\\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specialists&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;\\/div&gt;\\n\\n&lt;div&gt;Our consultants are specialized in either an industry or business function. This gives us a head start in understanding your requirements. We speed up your search for talent using our network amongst Vietnam\\u2019s best industry specialists, managers and executives.&lt;\\/div&gt;\\n\\n&lt;div&gt;Our day to day involvement right at the heart of the labor market enables us to support our clients with industry-specific benchmark information on compensation and benefits, demand and supply of talent and job-specific requirements. Our clients value our market expertise, our integrity and confidentiality standards and our focus on long term relationships.&lt;\\/div&gt;\\n\\n&lt;div&gt;Covering the whole labor market, we deliver a particular focus on the following industries:&lt;\\/div&gt;\\n\\n&lt;ol&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;FMCG&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Financial services&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;ICT&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&gt;Industrial &amp;amp; supply chain&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t&lt;li&