(1, 1, 'zO3AX7rZjh', 'Dành cho nhân viên', 'For employers', 'danh-cho-nhan-vien-zO3AX7rZjh', 'for-employers--zO3AX7rZjh', NULL, '<p>Welcome to Talentnet Executive Search Services. With more than 10 years of HR experience in setting international standards in the Vietnamese labor market, Talentnet’s dedicated Executive Search team has an unparalleled reach into this market. We deliver results by equipping experienced and driven consultants with state of the art technology. Working together with both large multinationals and well-regarded local companies, we are a renowned HR brand for both employers and professional talent. We are passionate about helping you find the professionals you need to deliver your business strategy.</p>\n\n<div><strong>Specialists</strong></div>\n\n<div>Our consultants are specialized in either an industry or business function. This gives us a head start in understanding your requirements. We speed up your search for talent using our network amongst Vietnam’s best industry specialists, managers and executives.</div>\n\n<div>Our day to day involvement right at the heart of the labor market enables us to support our clients with industry-specific benchmark information on compensation and benefits, demand and supply of talent and job-specific requirements. Our clients value our market expertise, our integrity and confidentiality standards and our focus on long term relationships.</div>\n\n<div>Covering the whole labor market, we deliver a particular focus on the following industries:</div>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>FMCG</li>\n	<li>Financial services</li>\n	<li>ICT</li>\n	<li>Industrial &amp; supply chain</li>\n	<li>Trading, sourcing &amp; retail</li>\n	<li>Petrochemical</li>\n	<li>Hospitality &amp; Education</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div>And on the following business functions</div>\n\n<ul type="disc">\n	<li>Sales/Marketing</li>\n	<li>Finance</li>\n	<li>Legal</li>\n	<li>Human resources</li>\n	<li>Support staff</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div><strong>Send us a mail with your request <a href="vi/dia-diem-van-phong"><span style="color: rgb(255, 102, 0);"><em>here</em></span></a> or call us direct at + 84 8 6291 4188.</strong></div>\n', '<p>Welcome to Talentnet Executive Search Services. With more than 10 years of HR experience in setting international standards in the Vietnamese labor market, Talentnet’s dedicated Executive Search team has an unparalleled reach into this market. We deliver results by equipping experienced and driven consultants with state of the art technology. Working together with both large multinationals and well-regarded local companies, we are a renowned HR brand for both employers and professional talent. We are passionate about helping you find the professionals you need to deliver your business strategy.</p>\n\n<div><strong>Specialists</strong></div>\n\n<div>Our consultants are specialized in either an industry or business function. This gives us a head start in understanding your requirements. We speed up your search for talent using our network amongst Vietnam’s best industry specialists, managers and executives.</div>\n\n<div>Our day to day involvement right at the heart of the labor market enables us to support our clients with industry-specific benchmark information on compensation and benefits, demand and supply of talent and job-specific requirements. Our clients value our market expertise, our integrity and confidentiality standards and our focus on long term relationships.</div>\n\n<div>Covering the whole labor market, we deliver a particular focus on the following industries:</div>\n\n<ul type="disc">\n	<li>FMCG</li>\n	<li>Financial services</li>\n	<li>ICT</li>\n	<li>Industrial &amp; supply chain</li>\n	<li>Trading, sourcing &amp; retail</li>\n	<li>Petrochemical</li>\n	<li>Hospitality &amp; Education</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div>And on the following business functions</div>\n\n<ul type="disc">\n	<li>Sales/Marketing</li>\n	<li>Finance</li>\n	<li>Legal</li>\n	<li>Human resources</li>\n	<li>Support staff</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div><strong>Send us a mail with your request <a href="en/office-locations"><span style="color: rgb(255, 102, 0);"><em>here</em></span></a> or call us direct at + 84 8 6291 4188.</strong></div>\n', 1, '2015-01-23 16:28:58', '2014-06-19 10:07:30'),
(2, 1, 'pM39R1YI1a', 'Dành cho các chuyên gia', 'For professionals', 'danh-cho-cac-chuyen-gia-pM39R1YI1aX', 'for-professionals--pM39R1YI1aX', NULL, '<p>Welcome to Talentnet Executive Search Services for professionals. Looking for a new job?</p>\n\n<div>Submit your resume, create an own account and be automatically considered for current and future vacancies, based on the criteria you yourself set.</div>\n\n<div>With more than 10 years of experience in setting international standards in the Vietnamese market, Talentnet’s dedicated Executive Search team has a wide-reaching network amongst Vietnam’s biggest multinationals and most well-regarded local companies.</div>\n\n<div><strong>From market update to career advice</strong></div>\n\n<div>What is the latest update on the job market? Is this the right time to make a move? How does my experience compare with current market demands? Thinking about a career switch? Our consultants are specialized in either an industry or business function. We will be glad to share our expertise with you to help you make the right decision, now or in the future.</div>\n\n<div><strong>Contact us at + 84 8 6291 41 88.</strong></div>\n', '<p>Welcome to Talentnet Executive Search Services for professionals. Looking for a new job?</p>\n\n<div>Submit your resume, create an own account and be automatically considered for current and future vacancies, based on the criteria you yourself set.</div>\n\n<div>With more than 10 years of experience in setting international standards in the Vietnamese market, Talentnet’s dedicated Executive Search team has a wide-reaching network amongst Vietnam’s biggest multinationals and most well-regarded local companies.</div>\n\n<div><strong>From market update to career advice</strong></div>\n\n<div>What is the latest update on the job market? Is this the right time to make a move? How does my experience compare with current market demands? Thinking about a career switch? Our consultants are specialized in either an industry or business function. We will be glad to share our expertise with you to help you make the right decision, now or in the future.</div>\n\n<div><strong>Contact us at + 84 8 6291 41 88.</strong></div>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:44:37', '2014-07-11 14:44:37'),
(3, 2, 'jhJxeG8yo0', 'Gia công phần mềm lương', 'Payroll Outsourcing', 'gia-cong-phan-mem-luong-jhJxeG8yo02', 'payroll-outsourcing--jhJxeG8yo02', NULL, '<p>Acting as your outsourced Compensation &amp; Benefits Division, TalentNet will provide you with a full payroll service. You will have a dedicated payroll officer, who will manage your workforces’ benefits using advanced software used by leading corporations.<br />\nTalentNet handles the entire payroll operation from start to finish. All you need to do is provide us with basic employee and payment data, approve the payroll and remit the amounts due to meet your payroll commitments. All the rest will be handled efficiently by our team.<br />\nHowever, if you only need part of the service, we offer you the flexibility of choosing which parts of the service you would like us to provide, from the following range of activities which make up the full outsourced payroll service:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nServices Offered</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Data entry<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Payroll processing<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Compulsory insurance : monthly reporting and remittance…<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Personal Income tax : monthly filling and annual finalization…<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tax calculation<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Additions and Deductions<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Termination payments<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reporting (for both Government and internal Management )<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pay-slip summaries<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Updates on labor law</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Acting as your outsourced Compensation &amp; Benefits Division, TalentNet will provide you with a full payroll service. You will have a dedicated payroll officer, who will manage your workforces’ benefits using advanced software used by leading corporations.<br />\nTalentNet handles the entire payroll operation from start to finish. All you need to do is provide us with basic employee and payment data, approve the payroll and remit the amounts due to meet your payroll commitments. All the rest will be handled efficiently by our team.<br />\nHowever, if you only need part of the service, we offer you the flexibility of choosing which parts of the service you would like us to provide, from the following range of activities which make up the full outsourced payroll service:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nServices Offered</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Data entry<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Payroll processing<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Compulsory insurance : monthly reporting and remittance…<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Personal Income tax : monthly filling and annual finalization…<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tax calculation<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Additions and Deductions<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Termination payments<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reporting (for both Government and internal Management )<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pay-slip summaries<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Updates on labor law</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:49:06', '2014-07-11 14:49:06'),
(4, 2, 'fOFmcTS0BO', 'Nhân viên chính quy', 'Staff Regularization', 'nhan-vien-chinh-quy-fOFmcTS0BOx', 'staff-regularization--fOFmcTS0BOx', NULL, '<p>We will provide a regularization service for the employment of candidates that you have already recruited. TalentNet will undertake the role of a “third party”, taking on the legal responsibilities to employees whom you have selected. In this capacity, we will deliver the following HR requirements:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Services Offered</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Signing the labor contract with the sucessful candidates</li>\n	<li>HR on-board Administration and Support</li>\n	<li>Payroll - Insurance – Taxation processing</li>\n	<li>Additions and Deductions</li>\n	<li>Maternity/Sick leave claims</li>\n	<li>Termination payments</li>\n	<li>Pay-slip summaries</li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>We will provide a regularization service for the employment of candidates that you have already recruited. TalentNet will undertake the role of a “third party”, taking on the legal responsibilities to employees whom you have selected. In this capacity, we will deliver the following HR requirements:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Services Offered</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Signing the labor contract with the sucessful candidates</li>\n	<li>HR on-board Administration and Support</li>\n	<li>Payroll - Insurance – Taxation processing</li>\n	<li>Additions and Deductions</li>\n	<li>Maternity/Sick leave claims</li>\n	<li>Termination payments</li>\n	<li>Pay-slip summaries</li>\n</ul>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:50:15', '2014-07-11 14:50:15'),
(5, 2, 'AfBX2QxXm6', 'Dịch vụ giải pháp nhân sự: Dành cho nguời sử dụng lao động', 'Staffing Solution Service: For employers', 'dich-vu-giai-phap-nhan-su-danh-cho-nguoi-su-dung-lao-dong-AfBX2QxXm6', 'staffing-solution-service-for-employers--AfBX2QxXm6', NULL, '<p>To allow you to focus on your core business activities, we can provide a complete staffing solutions package. This covers finding and recruiting employees for you, managing all labor–related issues during their employment, including labor management, insurance registration, personal income tax returns and year-end finalizations. We will also provide HR support and guidance to employees from the time they join until the time they leave, which will help maximize their effectiveness in their role.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Services Offered</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Search and selection of candidates based on companies’ requirements.</li>\n	<li>Provision of contractors to companies.</li>\n	<li>On going HR Administration and Support</li>\n	<li>Staff management</li>\n	<li>Payroll - Insurance – Taxation processing.</li>\n	<li>Additions and Deductions</li>\n	<li>Maternity/Sick leave claims</li>\n	<li>Termination payments</li>\n	<li>Pay-slip summaries</li>\n	<li>Provision of a replacement in the event of an employee resigning</li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>To allow you to focus on your core business activities, we can provide a complete staffing solutions package. This covers finding and recruiting employees for you, managing all labor–related issues during their employment, including labor management, insurance registration, personal income tax returns and year-end finalizations. We will also provide HR support and guidance to employees from the time they join until the time they leave, which will help maximize their effectiveness in their role.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Services Offered</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Search and selection of candidates based on companies’ requirements.</li>\n	<li>Provision of contractors to companies.</li>\n	<li>On going HR Administration and Support</li>\n	<li>Staff management</li>\n	<li>Payroll - Insurance – Taxation processing.</li>\n	<li>Additions and Deductions</li>\n	<li>Maternity/Sick leave claims</li>\n	<li>Termination payments</li>\n	<li>Pay-slip summaries</li>\n	<li>Provision of a replacement in the event of an employee resigning</li>\n</ul>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:54:09', '2014-07-11 14:52:10'),
(6, 2, 'NDve6AwD0a', 'Dịch vụ giải pháp nhân sự: Đối với ngừơi lao động', 'Staffing Solution Service: For employees', 'dich-vu-giai-phap-nhan-su-doi-voi-nguoi-lao-dong-NDve6AwD0at', 'staffing-solution-service-for-employees--NDve6AwD0at', NULL, '<p>If you are available…</p>\n\n<p>If you like flexible jobs, and have more time for traveling, enjoy other parts of your life..</p>\n\n<p>If you like to learn and develop from the jobs from different industries…</p>\n\n<p>If you like to experience the diversified of various Corporate culture..</p>\n\n<p>If you like to work part time for this moment because of personal plan…</p>\n\n<p>Please <a href="http://www.talentnet.vn/jobs/submit-cv"><strong>submit&nbsp; CV</strong></a> to us to win a job in below functions:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Administration</li>\n	<li>Accountant/ Finance</li>\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\n	<li>Logistic</li>\n	<li>Supply chain</li>\n	<li>And others…</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For more information, please contact: <a href="mailto:hroutsourcing@talentnet.vn">hroutsourcing@talentnet.vn</a>;&nbsp; (848) 62914188 ext 309.</p>\n', '<p>If you are available…</p>\n\n<p>If you like flexible jobs, and have more time for traveling, enjoy other parts of your life..</p>\n\n<p>If you like to learn and develop from the jobs from different industries…</p>\n\n<p>If you like to experience the diversified of various Corporate culture..</p>\n\n<p>If you like to work part time for this moment because of personal plan…</p>\n\n<p>Please <a href="http://www.talentnet.vn/jobs/submit-cv"><strong>submit&nbsp; CV</strong></a> to us to win a job in below functions:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Administration</li>\n	<li>Accountant/ Finance</li>\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\n	<li>Logistic</li>\n	<li>Supply chain</li>\n	<li>And others…</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For more information, please contact: <a href="mailto:hroutsourcing@talentnet.vn">hroutsourcing@talentnet.vn</a>;&nbsp; (848) 62914188 ext 309.</p>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:53:45', '2014-07-11 14:53:45'),
(7, 3, '5SS4xdrztK', 'Total Remuneration Survey (TRS)', 'Total Remuneration Survey (TRS)', 'total-remuneration-survey-trs-5SS4xdrztKx', 'total-remuneration-survey-trs--5SS4xdrztKx', NULL, '<p>Today''s Human Resource professionals are seeking solutions to build a consistent pay strategy. There is a need to maintain external competitiveness while maintaining internal equity. Mercer''s Total Remuneration Survey (TRS) collects compensation and typical benefits information to help you to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Gain understanding of key remuneration issues in your country</li>\n	<li>Evaluate the competitive position of your company</li>\n	<li>Access reliable, accurate and high quality market data anytime and anywhere through the web</li>\n	<li>Obtain customized statistics that meet your needs using a robust pay database</li>\n	<li>Make your pay packages more attractive by establishing competitive and cost effective compensation and benefits adjustments</li>\n	<li>Identify areas for improvement in your attraction and retention process</li>\n	<li>Plan compensation adjustments based on meaningful comparisons of remuneration practices</li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>Today''s Human Resource professionals are seeking solutions to build a consistent pay strategy. There is a need to maintain external competitiveness while maintaining internal equity. Mercer''s Total Remuneration Survey (TRS) collects compensation and typical benefits information to help you to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Gain understanding of key remuneration issues in your country</li>\n	<li>Evaluate the competitive position of your company</li>\n	<li>Access reliable, accurate and high quality market data anytime and anywhere through the web</li>\n	<li>Obtain customized statistics that meet your needs using a robust pay database</li>\n	<li>Make your pay packages more attractive by establishing competitive and cost effective compensation and benefits adjustments</li>\n	<li>Identify areas for improvement in your attraction and retention process</li>\n	<li>Plan compensation adjustments based on meaningful comparisons of remuneration practices</li>\n</ul>\n', 1, '2014-07-11 14:58:55', '2014-07-11 14:58:55');
